song of the west is a 1930 american pre-code drama film directed by george sherman and written by lillie hayward . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , betty furness , lucien littlefield , frank albertson , betty furness , lucien littlefield , lucien littlefield , lucien littlefield , lucien littlefield , irene rich , and frank mchugh . the film was released on december 25 , 1930 , by paramount pictures .